{"tid":1343803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［反擊鄉黑］超合作運動——舉報圍村僭建","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T20:26:54.000Z","uid":34914,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3bdcfa56d4232f05cebf871e38651998c1b1c2","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:31:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">超合作運動&mdash;&mdash;舉報圍村僭建</span><br />\n<br />\n僭建唔單止有違法例，分分鐘破壞樓宇結構，造成危樓，或倒塌風險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為良好市民，舉報僭建，你我有責。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不遵從清拆僭建物的法定命令，會有什麼後果？<br />\n<br />\n如業主不遵從命令，屋宇署會委託政府承建商代為清拆，其後向業主悉數追討工程費用，另加監督費及附加費。<br />\n<br />\n不遵從法定命令屬刑事罪行，最高刑罰為監禁1年及罰款港幣20萬元。如違法情況持續，另處罰款每天港幣2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處亦會記錄有關命令。物業如有按揭，相關的財務機構會獲知有關命令。<br />\n<br />\n地址：<br />\n九龍油麻地海庭道11<br />\n號西九龍政府合署北座<br />\n屋宇署總部地下<br />\n<br />\n一般查詢、舉報及投訴<br />\n屋宇署熱線<br />\n2626 1616（由「1823」接聽）<br />\n<br />\n網上舉報<br />\n<a href=\"https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feform.one.gov.hk%2Fform%2Fbd0001%2Ftc%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=725c74b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eform.one.gov.hk/form/bd0001/tc/</a><br />\n<br />\n（資料來源：屋宇署）"},{"pid":"d83a2d4fcca322e87ff8d0b232865c279ef07dba","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:31:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f94528a805ab2fa95ff9df0a49dfdfad271c70a0","tid":1343803,"uid":36911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:33:25.000Z","msg":"無用<br />\n屋宇署都唔敢入村啦"},{"pid":"9f450098da679cb2605eb2e52c38ba0c8172c8e6","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94528a805ab2fa95ff9df0a49dfdfad271c70a0","tid":1343803,"uid":36911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:33:25.000Z","msg":"無用<br />\n屋宇署都唔敢入村啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:37:08.000Z","msg":"至少逼屋宇署落簿"},{"pid":"b2e57bf92c4025825920b745058c3d6fa30c02f2","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:41:43.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥：不會特赦村屋僭建<br />\n<br />\n2011年11月29日 13:31<br />\n<br />\n政府表示處理新界村屋僭建問題，絕不會有特赦。對於新界村民焚燒發展局局長林鄭月娥的紙紮公仔洩憤，林鄭月娥表示會以平常心看待，若感到人身安全受威脅，會尋求警方介入。<br />\n<br />\n新界村民群起抗議，不滿政府清拆僭建物的做法。政府強調，有危險的村屋僭建物，又或是在今年6月28日或以後，才興建的僭建物，必須取締。<br />\n<br />\n對於鄉議局主席劉皇發揚言以拖字訣，等到新一屆政府上任才繼續商討，林鄭月娥表示，會依法辦事，不可以再拖延下去。<br />\n<br />\n對於村民以焚燒紙紮公仔、棺木，及清拆僭建物的小冊子洩憤，林鄭月娥說，暫時未感到安全受威脅，有需要時會請警方介入。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，當屋宇署人員進入新界清拆僭建物時遇到困難，同樣是找當區的警員協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=18858&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D18858%26refer%3D&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcnfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3aa88dcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D18858%26refer%3D&h=2931ce55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=18858&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"c359831952efb7d52c1609517e98dfd5bc2932c3","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:42:16.000Z","msg":"支持特首打擊僭建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c6041e546f95ba356bea86888bff94b2706bc8","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:55:17.000Z","msg":"推啊！作為奉公守法嘅良好市民，應該舉報違規人仕！"},{"pid":"9233b11884e54d2c9ef4e26c8a28d8faaedbdd90","tid":1343803,"uid":34914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:00:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44140ced0d46b6f56f36179f5c901441bfe5e00e","tid":1343803,"uid":218193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:02:29.0